snippet.title: F-ZERO 99 - Nintendo Switch Online - Nintendo Direct 9.14.2023
snippet.description:
F-ZERO 99 is available today for active Nintendo Switch Online members: https://www.nintendo.com/switch/online/

The F-ZERO game returns as a 99-player battle royale! Race on classic F-ZERO courses with machines from the original Super NES game and tear through courses in high-speed races. But be careful, your Power Meter will decrease if you crash into pilots or guard rails. If it hits zero, you're out!

#FZERO99 #NintendoSwitch #NintendoSwitchOnline #NintendoDirect
